|Form                  |Notation               |
|----------------------|-----------------------|
|Atomic binary relation|`[A —op→ B]_{w,c,t}`   |
|Hyperrelation         |`⟨op : e₁, e₂, …, eₙ⟩` |
|Composition           |`[A→B] ∘ [B→C] = [A→C]`|
|Merge                 |`r₁ ⊕ r₂`              |
|Contextual binding    |`r ⊗ frame`            |
|Analogy               |`r₁ ~ r₂`              |
|Conflict              |`r ⊥ s`                |
|Entailment            |`r ⊢ s`                |
|Constraint            |`r ⊣ s`                |
|Coherence             |`Φ(L) ≡ Φ(R)`          |

